direnv-hook(1) -- shell hook installation utility
=================================================

## SYNOPSIS

`direnv hook $0`

## DESCRIPTION

Small utility function to install the shell hook in your .bashrc or .zshrc

## USAGE

in ~/.bashrc or ~/.zshrc :

    eval `direnv hook $0`

put it at the end to make sure it doesn't interfere with the rest.

## SEE ALSO

direnv(1)
